flowchart TD
    A([Customer Arrives]) --> B{Is queue length > Balk Threshold?}
    B -- Yes --> C([Customer Balks / Leaves])
    B -- No --> D[Join Shortest Cashier Queue]
    
    D --> E{Patience Exceeded while waiting?}
    E -- Yes --> F([Customer Reneges / Leaves])
    E -- No --> G[Reach Cashier: Order & Pay]
    
    G --> H{Dine-in or Takeout?}
    G -. Order Sent .-> K[[Barista Queue / Prepares Drink]]
    
    H -- Takeout --> I[Wait in Takeout Pickup Area]
    H -- Dine-In --> J[Sit at Dine-in Table]
    
    I --> L[Order Completed & Served]
    J --> L
    K -. Drink Ready .-> L
    
    L --> M([Customer Departs])
